{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place simmering basket on mixing bowl lid. Weigh into simmering basket carrots followed by onions, then courgettes. Set simmering basket aside.","Place garlic, anchovy, basil and parsley in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add olive oil and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b> to make a pesto.","Add tomatoes, salt and pepper then mix well with spatula.","Dip a piece of baking paper in water and use it to line Varoma tray. Place trout fillets on prepared Varoma tray and cover them with tomato and pesto mixture.","Place water in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket, insert Varoma tray and place covered Varoma into position. Choose cooking time for thinner or thicker fillets and cook <b>18-22 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>.","Set Varoma aside and remove simmering basket with aid of spatula. Arrange trout and vegetables on a large serving plate and drizzle olive oil over the top before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["130 g carrots, cut in slices (5 mm)","100 g onions, cut in bite-size pieces","200 g courgettes, halved lengthways and cut in slices (1 cm)","1 garlic clove","1 anchovy, tinned","20 g fresh basil leaves","30 g fresh parsley","50 g olive oil, plus extra for serving","200 g cherry tomatoes","1 pinch fine sea salt","¼ tsp freshly ground black pepper","4 trout fillets, skinned (approx. 150 g each)","600 g water"]}],"id":"r80563","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-qcA13ZXFWc0\/XZVPwdzbjXI\/AAAAAAAAc8M\/BV7P_sGc76AC-QBzl6yH1ShiksISI-digCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Dxe1hgrwVSdOuMU5.png","title":"Trout with Pesto, Tomatoes and Vegetables","publishedAt":"2015-05-13T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"34.7 g","fat":"21.6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"7.7 g","calories":"1521 kJ \/ 364 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking paper","basicInfo":["easy","15m","45m","4 portions"]}